data.title: Orchestra Journal
data.meta_description: Orchestra journal - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is the preface to an issue of the journal "Orchestra" published in 2018. It summarizes the activities of the Central Eastern European WASBE Association in 2017, including international competitions, conferences, and festivals held in various member countries. It thanks the chairmen and members for their contributions and active work promoting wind band music. It also congratulates the journal on its 50th anniversary and recognizes its important role in sharing information about orchestral ensembles.
